  "body": "If you want to build a front-end that doesn't use the sdk functionality, but just wants to know the values in [chain-constants.ts](packages/sdk/src/utils/chain-constants.ts) there is no way to get these values.\r\n\r\nRight now you have to copy and past these configuration values into your repo.\r\n\r\nIt would be ideal if you can do:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport { chainConstants } from '@eth-optimism/sdk'\r\n\r\nconst getl1BridgeMessenger = (l2ChainId: number) => {\r\n  return chainConstants[l2ChainId].L1CrossDomainMessenger;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut right now `chainConstants` is not exported from the package.",
